data.description: Beautiful condo in the popular gated community of Regatta Pointe. You will LOVE the location and lifestyle this will offer, as you will be close walking distance to ASU, Mill Avenue, Tempe Town Lake & right next door to favorite Tempe spots The Lodge, Culinary Dropout & The Shop Beer Co. Located on the top floor with great views of Tempe, this home has been updated over recent years & is completly move in ready. Updated flooring, bathrooms, appliances, windows, lighting & more. This unit has a large, rare storage area connected to your private garage too! Regatta Pointe is a wonderful community with a resort style pool, fitness center, community room, BBQ area and more.This is PERFECT for someone living Tempe or for an investor that wants an incredible investment property close to campus!
